    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting perspective. So, if I'm teaching this, should I frame it to the students that the primary purpose of the Due Process Clause is to act as this safeguard for these evolving liberties? I want them to understand that it's a vital, living part of our legal framework that ensures progress, rather than just a procedural checklist for the government.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
